        "app_name": "The Wire Loop Game VR",
        "release_date": "1980-01-01T00:00:00.000Z",
        "description": "The Wire Loop Game VR brings this traditional well known game into virtual reality. By default the right controller is used, but if you wish to use the left hand, then turn the right controller off.\n\nThe aim of the game is to guide the metal hoop along the length of the wire without it touching. If it touches the wire, then the buzzer will sound and you will fail. In this version of the game there is also a time limit to complete the wire in. You can adjust the height of the wire by sliding a control on the table, in order to accommodate different player heights and preferences.\n\nThis game will require concentration, focus and dexterity in order to complete all the wires. You will also need a steady hand as shaking may cause you to fail. There are 50 wires to complete.\n\nWARNING: This game may be the most frustrating game you have played in VR! ",
